data.description: Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this 3-bed, 3-bath haven in Gig Harbor, Washington, offers an idyllic lifestyle just steps from the water. Durable laminate flooring graces the main level, comprising a family room, dining area, kitchen, and a versatile den/office. The expansive back deck presents views on Stansberry Lake, an ideal spot for both relaxation and entertaining. The upstairs retreat boasts an extra-large primary bedroom with a 5-piece ensuite and walk-in closet, plus two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a bonus room. The fully fenced backyard with a shed, a 26-foot garage with storage, and large parking perfect for an RV are just a few features that enhance both comfort and practicality.
